have seven or eight kids

307
00:39:13,165 --> 00:39:15,759
Seven or eight? Is that all?
- Yes, don't I need to work?

308
00:39:15,834 --> 00:39:18,098
But I'll send them over
to you for stories

309
00:39:18,270 --> 00:39:21,103
