- No Jai

316
00:39:40,892 --> 00:39:46,159
I relate every place, every
thing in this city with you

317
00:39:47,165 --> 00:39:50,157
I may stay away from you, but I
can't tear myself apart from you

318
00:39:54,172 --> 00:39:57,835
I must go now... else I'll
miss my flight, too

319
00:39:58,176 --> 00:39:59,837
You are...

320
00:40:00,912 --> 00:40:02,174
leaving right now?

321
00:40:03,181 --> 00:40:05,843
