I know, you think I'm selfish

324
00:40:16,228 --> 00:40:20,892
But today... please
let me be selfish

325
00:40:22,234 --> 00:40:25,397
Let me escort you to the airport.
- No

326
00:40:26,238 --> 00:40:27,899
I'll go alone

327
00:40:27,973 --> 00:40:29,907
You are not going alone that far.
- No, Jai

328
00:40:31,243 --> 00:40:33,234
Please don't make it
more difficult for me

329
00:40:41,019 --> 00:40:42,452
I will miss you.

330
00:40:43,288 --> 00:40:44,949
I love you.

331
00:40:46,291 --> 00:40:52,958
Bye. - Stupid.

332
00:41:24,029 --> 00:41:25,291
Neha...?

333
00:41:41,646 --> 00:41:45,980
What are you doing?
Neha, what are you..

334
00:41:56,361 --> 00:41:59,023
Have you gone mad, Neha?
What's happening here?

335
00:41:59,097 --> 00:42:01,964
What's the matter?
- I...

336
00:42:06,238 --> 00:42:07,296
What is it?

337
00:42:19,351 --> 00:42:24,311
How would you know that you're in
love with a criminal's daughter?

338
00:42:27,092 --> 00:42:29,356
A criminal?
- Yes

339
00:42:32,364 --> 00:42:39,031
Daddy's no more. But he left
making life difficult for me.

340
00:42:40,105 --> 00:42:42,039
What does that mean?

341
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:49,046
Daddy had borrowed money
from the underworld...

342
00:42:49,114 --> 00:42:51,048
and now, they're following me

343
00:42:53,418 --> 00:42:57,047
Till now, they only kept
threatening me. But now...

344
00:42:57,155 --> 00:43:02,024
they say that if I don't return
their money within 3 days, they will...

345
00:43:05,096 --> 00:43:09,032
they will kidnap me.
- Who do they think they are?

346
00:43:10,368 --> 00:43:13,030
They're like the wolves,
Jai. I don't..

347
00:43:13,104 --> 00:43:17,040
..want to fall in their
hands. So I...

348
00:43:21,112 --> 00:43:23,046
Didn't you consider for
a moment what would..

349
00:43:23,114 --> 00:43:26,083
..happen of me if you were harmed?

350
00:43:28,420 --> 00:43:32,754
Don't worry. Just tell me
where I will find them

351
00:43:32,824 --> 00:43:37,420
They're very dangerous, Jai. I did
all I could to repay them, but...

352
00:43:37,495 --> 00:43:42,432
Don't worry, I can really help. I
have the money. 2.5 million in cash

353
00:43:44,436 --> 00:43:50,102
It isn't so little.
I owe them 60 million.

354
00:43:59,484 --> 00:44:02,044
Neha, everything is going to be fine.

355
00:44:03,154 --> 00:44:05,088
I'll deal with everything.
You don't worry

356
00:44:13,431 --> 00:44:18,095
It's five years old,
but thank God...

357
00:44:18,169 --> 00:44:24,108
you've maintained it rather well.
You also have a 24-hour water supply

358
00:44:24,175 --> 00:44:27,110
Got to sell immediately, right?
So, thank God...

359
00:44:27,178 --> 00:44:30,443
it'll fetch at least 8 million.
Is that okay?

360
00:44:31,216 --> 00:44:33,150
Don't worry.

361
00:44:34,486 --> 00:44:38,115
Nice, nice... looks solid

362
00:44:39,491 --> 00:44:44,155
Facing the West. Also
has a nice sea-view?

363
00:44:44,229 --> 00:44:47,824
Can we get a glimpse of
the sea from here? - No

364
00:44:47,899 --> 00:44:50,163
No? From the terrace?

365
00:44:50,502 --> 00:44:53,164
No harm in saying you can

366
00:44:53,505 --> 00:44:57,669
Since it's the ground floor,
security is good enough

367
00:44:59,511 --> 00:45:04,448
This is a weak lock, I say. But
that's okay. I'll handle it

368
00:45:04,549 --> 00:45:08,610
Actually, I have a buyer.
And cash won't be a problem

369
00:45:09,487 --> 00:45:12,149
I'm sure it'll get sold at 5 million

370
00:45:12,223 --> 00:45:14,157
You want me to negotiate?

371
00:45:16,494 --> 00:45:18,826
60 million? You can't be serious!

372
00:45:19,230 --> 00:45:23,166
You say 60 millions as if you
were borrowing my car for 6 days

373
00:45:27,238 --> 00:45:30,173
60 million. Only
one way of raising that..

374
00:45:30,241 --> 00:45:32,175
..type of money in
such a short time

375
00:45:32,243 --> 00:45:34,177
Go and rob a bank!

376
00:45:35,246 --> 00:45:39,205
Stop joking.
- Sorry, sorry.... but 60 million?!

377
00:45:40,285 --> 00:45:42,845
Are you mad? You will rob a bank...?

378
00:45:42,954 --> 00:45:46,219
What else can we do? We
have no other choice

379
00:45:46,291 --> 00:45:54,221
Your house and mine and our belongings
won't fetch more than 20 million.

380
00:45:56,568 --> 00:45:59,230
I know what I'll do. I'll go to
the bank tomorrow morning and...

381
00:45:59,571 --> 00:46:03,166
Really...? By the way, which
bank do you propose to rob?

382
00:46:03,508 --> 00:46:08,673
Standard Chartered Bank, Bandra.
Now listen to me, Neha

383
00:46:09,514 --> 00:46:13,177
I know what I'm doing is wrong.
But we have no other choice

384
00:46:13,551 --> 00:46:16,179
To raise 60 million in just
two days... think about it

385
00:46:18,289 --> 00:46:22,225
We've tried everything, we...
- Rather I die than do this, Jai

386
00:46:22,727 --> 00:46:27,721
Listen to me, Neha

387
00:46:29,300 --> 00:46:31,234
Neha, just stop.

388
00:46:35,306 --> 00:46:39,242
Promise me, you won't even joke
about such a thing again

389
00:46:40,411 --> 00:46:45,747
If something happens to you... -
Okay. The bank robbery's off. Okay?

390
00:47:29,627 --> 00:47:33,290
Five guards during the day. Must
at least be 3 during the night

391
00:47:33,364 --> 00:47:35,798
Looks pretty difficult

392
00:47:37,635 --> 00:47:43,301
Mr. Vikram, it's great pleasure
to be of service to you.

393
00:47:43,374 --> 00:47:49,313
What urgency makes you withdraw
70 million in one go?

394
00:47:49,380 --> 00:47:53,339
No problem. The bank is
yours. So are we...

395
00:47:53,418 --> 00:47:57,684
and most important, the
money's yours too!

396
00:47:58,022 --> 00:48:02,959
Thank you for using our services.

397
00:48:03,027 --> 00:48:06,292
This is the first time we're handling
such a big wire-transfer for you

398
00:48:06,364 --> 00:48:09,299
I hope you will give us
the opportunity to..

399
00:48:09,367 --> 00:48:12,803
..do many more wire-transfers
for you

400
00:48:12,870 --> 00:48:15,304
Thank you very much.

401
00:48:35,026 --> 00:48:37,358
Seems I won't be required to
break the promise made to Neha.

402
00:48:37,428 --> 00:48:40,363
Now not the bank but
he is going to get robbed.

403
00:51:42,647 --> 00:51:46,105
You look well-bred. Why
did you come here?

404
00:51:48,686 --> 00:51:50,620
To steal

405
00:51:50,688 --> 00:51:52,622
I see

406
00:51:52,957 --> 00:51:57,621
I went to rob the bank and saw
you withdrawing the money

407
00:51:58,963 --> 00:52:00,624
Thought I'd rob it from you

408
00:52:06,904 --> 00:52:10,567
Robbing the bank was much
easier, wasn't it?

409
00:52:12,910 --> 00:52:14,571
Please, come in.

410
00:52:24,689 --> 00:52:28,625
What if you had got killed?

411
00:52:30,962 --> 00:52:32,623
That's okay

412
00:52:35,700 --> 00:52:37,634
I don't care for my life

413
00:52:37,969 --> 00:52:39,630
I'd at least have got 60 million.

414
00:52:42,974 --> 00:52:44,635
Why do you need the money?

415
00:52:44,709 --> 00:52:46,643
I don't consider it
necessary to tell you

416
00:52:46,711 --> 00:52:48,645
That's my problem.

417
00:52:51,749 --> 00:52:57,688
All right, you can tell
the cops when they arrive

418
00:53:16,974 --> 00:53:19,636
Have some juice. - No thanks.

419
00:53:20,711 --> 00:53:22,645
Have it. It's said
to be good for health

420
00:53:26,017 --> 00:53:27,644
Sit down

421
00:53:39,764 --> 00:53:43,700
It was six months ago that I
saw Neha for the first time..

422
00:53:59,817 --> 00:54:03,685
Interesting.. very very interesting.

423
00:54:08,025 --> 00:54:11,688
Let's say I give it to you.
I give you 60 million

424
00:54:17,768 --> 00:54:20,703
But what can I give you in return?

425
00:54:20,771 --> 00:54:22,705
Your life

426
00:54:22,773 --> 00:54:25,708
Something you don't care for, right?

427
00:54:28,779 --> 00:54:30,713
Which means...?

428
00:54:33,084 --> 00:54:36,713
Now look, Jai. There's
no going back after..

429
00:54:36,821 --> 00:54:39,756
..I tell you what I
am about to tell you.

430
00:54:39,824 --> 00:54:42,759
So think it over and...
- I'm prepared to do anything

431
00:54:42,827 --> 00:54:46,763
But I need the money. In 24 hours

432
00:54:48,833 --> 00:54:51,097
Are you sure? - Yeah.

433
00:54:51,168 --> 00:54:55,764
So listen. Maybe you've heard
of the internet robbery case?

434
00:54:56,107 --> 00:54:59,270
Yes, in which someone
stole 5.5 billion..

435
00:54:59,343 --> 00:55:01,208
..from Babu Anna's account, right?

436
00:55:04,048 --> 00:55:07,711
For 60 million, you must claim
to be the computer hacker...

437
00:55:07,818 --> 00:55:12,755
and turn yourself over to
the police. - But what..

438
00:55:12,823 --> 00:55:14,757
..will you gain out of it?

439
00:55:15,092 --> 00:55:16,753
Gain?

440
00:55:18,829 --> 00:55:25,758
I'll be rid of the fear of getting
caught or dying at Babu Anna's hands

441
00:55:26,437 --> 00:55:30,271
Because I am the computer
hacker, Jai

442
00:55:34,445 --> 00:55:37,778
I've committed a crime in
my lust for wealth...

443
00:55:37,848 --> 00:55:41,807
but I've lost my sleep
and peace of mind

444
00:55:46,157 --> 00:55:51,322
You were willing to lose your
life for 60 million, Jai

445
00:55:53,898 --> 00:55:55,832
Now you've only got
to serve a sentence

446
00:56:05,843 --> 00:56:07,777
What are you thinking about, Jai?

447
00:56:11,882 --> 00:56:15,318
Okay, not 60 million. I'll
give you 70 million...

448
00:56:17,154 --> 00:56:20,317
to spend the rest of your life,
after your imprisonment

449
00:56:20,391 --> 00:56:21,824
I agree

450
00:56:22,893 --> 00:56:24,827
Good boy.

451
00:56:24,895 --> 00:56:28,160
But I need just 60
million and not 70.

452
00:56:29,900 --> 00:56:31,834
All right. suit yourself

453
00:56:32,903 --> 00:56:36,168
When are you going to surrender?
- When are you going to pay me?

454
00:56:37,341 --> 00:56:40,333
Surrender. And you
will have the money

455
00:56:40,411 --> 00:56:42,845
Give me the money.
And I'll surrender

456
00:56:47,218 --> 00:56:49,345
Ok, fair enough.

457
00:56:49,954 --> 00:56:55,392
I think I can trust you
Where will you go anyway?

458
00:56:57,962 --> 00:57:02,160
Let's go inside. It takes a hell of
a lot of time to count 60 million.

459
00:57:07,905 --> 00:57:10,840
Throw this money in their face

460
00:57:14,912 --> 00:57:16,846
So much of money...? How?

461
00:57:18,949 --> 00:57:20,883
I've mortgaged my life to someone

462
