You think your boyfriend
is worth nothing!

463
00:57:27,958 --> 00:57:29,892
Been dealing in imported
cars for 3 years now..

464
00:57:29,960 --> 00:57:31,894
..I command respect too, no?

465
00:57:34,231 --> 00:57:35,892
All in one night...?

466
00:57:37,234 --> 00:57:41,398
One moment. You haven't really
robbed the bank...?

467
00:57:41,472 --> 00:57:43,906
Swear it on you!
I didn't rob the bank

468
00:57:45,242 --> 00:57:47,233
You've sworn on me.
- Sworn on you

469
00:57:47,311 --> 00:57:48,903
I didn't rob the bank. Okay?

470
00:57:48,979 --> 00:57:51,413
How we will we repay
such a huge debt?

471
00:57:52,616 --> 00:57:59,283
This is nothing. I'd give my
life for you, if I had to

472
00:58:00,024 --> 00:58:04,893
For as long as I live, it's
my duty to look after you

473
00:58:06,964 --> 00:58:10,559
Why must you talk about dying?
Our lives have only just begun

474
00:58:17,241 --> 00:58:18,902
What's that?

475
00:58:22,246 --> 00:58:26,410
Keep it with you forever.
And whatever happens...

476
00:58:28,285 --> 00:58:30,913
remember, I'm always with you

477
00:58:42,299 --> 00:58:43,960
I love you, Jai.

478
00:58:46,036 --> 00:58:48,129
I'm very scared, Jai

479
00:58:49,306 --> 00:58:54,300
I feel as if you're hiding
something from me

480
00:58:57,047 --> 00:59:00,016
Silly girl. Have I
ever lied to you?
